description:
Welcome to the Monster Hunter Wilds Showcase, presented by Monster Hunter Wilds producer, Ryozo Tsujimoto!

This showcase features exciting new information and reveals, including the latest trailer and more! If you've been wanting to play Monster Hunter Wilds ahead of the launch on February 28, 2025, you'll definitely want to check this out!

The newest addition to the Monster Hunter series, Monster Hunter Wilds will launch worldwide on PlayStation®5 on Friday, February 28, 2025. Pre-order now!
